longBusinessSummary: Kontigo Care AB (publ) provides health care solutions for addiction treatment in Sweden. It offers Previct Alcohol, a digital medical device for the treatment of alcohol addiction; Previct Gamble, a digital tool for the treatment of gambling addiction; Previct Drugs, a digital platform to stop drug addiction; Previct Mind, a modern tool used as support in the treatment of mental illness; Previct Family, a tool for the whole family when the whole family is in contact with a therapist for family's well-being; Previct Work, a digital supports that are used in addiction care at the workplace. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Uppsala, Sweden.
